NetworkManager-openvpn: NetworkManager-openvpn (NetworkManager vpn OpenVpn plugin)
NetworkManager-openvpn:
NetworkManager-openvpn: NetworkManager attempts to make networking invisible. When moving 
NetworkManager-openvpn: into areas you've been before, NetworkManager automatically connects 
NetworkManager-openvpn: to the last network the user chose to connect to. Likewise, when 
NetworkManager-openvpn: back at the desk, NetworkManager will switch to the faster, more 
NetworkManager-openvpn: reliable wired network connection. 
NetworkManager-openvpn:
NetworkManager-openvpn: This package contains vpn plugins for NetworkManager to allow easy
NetworkManager-openvpn: access to virtual private networks via OpenVpn. 
NetworkManager-openvpn:
